This paper discusses the integration of NFV and SDN technologies in network architecture, which falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). The paper also addresses issues related to reliability, performance, and scalability, which are relevant to systems and control (cs.SY) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses the design and synthesis of architectural designs, which is relevant to software engineering (cs.SE) and computer architecture (cs.AR).
